# Agentic Starter Cursor Router

Before answering or editing in this repo, read:

- `.agent/Instructions.md`: agent behavior rules
- `.agent/Context.md`: product, team, stack, current decisions
- `.agent/Memory.md`: user preferences, repeated corrections, operating memory

Cursor does not run the Claude Code hook chain. Treat this rule and `AGENTS.md` as the Cursor entrypoint, then read the `.agent` files directly.

Use code-review-graph MCP for code structure questions before broad text search. Use `docs/wiki/decisions/` and `docs/wiki/guides/` for decision rationale and operating rules.

After agentic/wiki/router changes, run:

```bash
bash scripts/verify-agent-ssot.sh
git diff --check
```

Important guide, ADR, or postmortem changes require a Review Gate Quiz with at most three questions. Long workflows require a snapshot under `docs/wiki/postmortem/temp/`.
